{"title":"联系方式预留","time":"2022 年 6 月 27 日","shareable":true,"id":"guide/traffic/train/contact","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"info","text":["受到新冠疫情的影响，为做好新冠肺炎疫情常态化防控同时便于乘车人及时接收到列车运行变更信息，旅客在购买火车票时，需要预留乘车人本人的手机号码并通过系统核验。"]},{"tag":"text","type":"warning","text":["未完成联系方式核验的人员，无法购买车票。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"预留与核验途径"},{"tag":"ul","heading":"线上","text":["铁路 12306APP","铁路 12306 微信公众号","中国铁路微信公众号","铁路 12306 支付宝小程序"]},{"tag":"ul","heading":"线下","text":["自动售票机","人工售票窗口","代售点"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/traffic/train/contact-app.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/traffic/train/contact-wechat-1.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/traffic/train/contact-wechat-2.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/traffic/train/contact-terminal.jpg"}]}